<br>
Fingers: Get a Shadel Bandti Ring from Fungus Grove Luclin. AC 6, 55 HP/Mana, 5 CR, 10 DR<br>
<br>
Waist: Brell's Girdle?<br>
<br>
Upgrade all you non Shining to Shining armor, I assume your guild can help with this.<br>
<br>
I will show my ignorance and say I never heard of a Brell's Girdle. In Maiden's Eye in Luclin there us a belt that drop off the four armed Centien mobs in the Ahkeva Ruins enrtry building called an Axgoreth's Belt of Defense. AC 20, +15 Wis/Str. No Drop. Can usually get one per camp of 4-5 hours. Depending on the stats of yoru Brell's it may be an upgrade path.<br>
<br>
As for the ret of your gear your in pretty good shape still. Upgrades at your level are almost all no drop from raid level mobs, so you know how to get those already.<br>
<br>
As a side note, if you have not done so, take a look at www.Magelo.com . They have a nice system there a lot of people are using to list their gear online. Make posts like this a lot easier to type. Take a look and see if it is your kinda thing. If you click on my name you will see an example of mine.<br>
<br>
Welcome back.<br>
