<br>
Depending on what your guild is doing, if you can get CoV faction, I would pick up some Bracers of Benevolence.<br>
<br>
Similarly, if you think you can bag Lodizal, work on eyepatch of plunder. (Although with our self haste spell, you would just be getting for stats. If your guild is doing tov, you might just wait for a mask there, the ik mask is usually unwanted and not bad).<br>
<br>
You might also want to check the stats of some of the armor drops in Umbral. For your non-shining pieces, those would likely be upgrades.<br>
<br>
Otherwise, you seem to be doing pretty good other than uber drops.<br>
