<br>
Spider Fur Belt is pretty darn common, AC 10, +5 Dex and Agil and I think 40 HP, Wt 0, drops in Velketor's Labyrinth. Run about 1000 plat.<br>
<br>
Smiter's Girdle, AC 10, +3 Str/Dex/Stam/Agil/Wis/Int/Cha, weight 0.1 From a Luclin mob, but I do not know which or where though.<br>
<br>
Magoomba's Girdle, of a mob in the Tenebrous Mountains, AC 11, +5 Str, +8 Dex, +4 Wis, + some miner resistsm weight 2.5.<br>
<br>
All are droppable, buyable and/or campable. The Axgoreth belt is only campable as no drop.<br>
<br>
Maidens Eye (Luclin zone) Vampires and boss mobs drop a few VERY nice AC 15 range idols all superior to the Idol of the Thorned. Plus most of them are undead so Instrument of Nife becomes REAL useful. It is amazing in mobs abd drops for an outside zone. <p><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=105286">Gilfalas Elaandrin</a>, Lvl 59 Knight of Tunare & Defender of Nature<br>
